law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 450, sec. 79, effective July 15, 1983. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. II, sec. 9(1). -- Amended 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 185, sec. 3. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1992b-32.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Contracts for capital outlay or printing in anticipation of appropriations.
